properties.headline: Winter Weather Advisory issued February 16 at 4:13AM AKST until February 18 at 6:00AM AKST by NWS Fairbanks, AK
properties.description:
* WHAT...Snow and blowing snow expected. Plan on difficult travel
conditions. Total snow accumulations of 3 to 6 inches are
expected. Visibility may be reduced to one half mile or less at
times.

* WHERE...Yukon Delta.

* WHEN...6 PM today to 6 AM Tuesday.

* ADDITIONAL DETAILS...Winds gusting as high as 35 mph will
cause areas of blowing and drifting snow.
properties.instruction:
A Winter Weather Advisory for snow and blowing snow means periods
of snow and blowing snow will cause travel difficulties.

NWSheadline: WINTER WEATHER ADVISORY IN EFFECT FROM 6 PM THIS EVENING TO 6 AM AKST TUESDAY
